name: ALLINDOGE
description: ALLINDOGE is building AgentOS, a next-generation AI operating system that breaks down the wall between Web2 and Web3 and builds a unified intelligent interaction layer. Users don't need to pay attention to complicated technical details, the system realizes seamless connection and collaboration between on-chain protocols and off-chain services with the help of advanced cross-chain technology and intelligent routing. You only need to express your real intention, and AI can intelligently analyze the demand, plan the optimal execution path, automatically complete cross-chain, cross-protocol and cross-platform operations, and continuously optimize the strategy according to the market dynamics.
